<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background-color: #eef4ff;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.12);
            border: 1px solid #dbe7ff;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dbe7ff;
        }

        .header h2 {
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #334155;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.25);
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #64748b;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        a {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Verify Your Email Address</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="message">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>
                Thank you for registering on our website. To complete your signup process and activate your account,
                please verify your email address by clicking the button below.
            </p>
            <p style="text-align: center; color:#ffffff">
                <a href="http://localhost:5173/verify?token={{token}}" target="_blank"
                    style="display: inline-block; padding:12px 24px; background-color:#2563eb; color:#ffffff !important; text-decoration:none; border-radius:8px; font-weight:bold;">
                    Verify Your Email
                </a>
            </p>
            <p>If you did not initiate this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 Collab Flow. All Rights Reserved.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>